1
00:00:05,057 --> 00:00:09,484
If in this world
we’re constantly searching

2
00:00:09,484 --> 00:00:13,134
for ideals in terms
of the most beautiful,

3
00:00:13,134 --> 00:00:14,834
the most sweet, 
the most charming,
 

4
00:00:14,834 --> 00:00:17,584
the most affectionate, 
the most loving …

5
00:00:17,834 --> 00:00:21,186
[Absolute Soulmate]

6
00:00:21,186 --> 00:00:26,910
the person who could be considered
my best counterpart;

7
00:00:26,910 --> 00:00:33,719
an ideal representation of beauty, 
charm, sweetness, love, and affection,

8
00:00:33,719 --> 00:00:39,259
of what is to be seen, heard, felt,
tasted, touched and smelled.

9
00:00:39,259 --> 00:00:42,677
What if that
is the ultimate reality?

10
00:00:42,677 --> 00:00:46,905
Instead we’re being told
that the ultimate source of everything

11
00:00:46,905 --> 00:00:52,718
is something impersonal 
and maybe unconscious.

12
00:00:52,718 --> 00:00:57,446
So that which is dead 
and unconscious
 

13
00:00:57,446 --> 00:01:00,446
is giving life
to so many conscious beings;

14
00:01:00,446 --> 00:01:05,379
what cannot see 
is gifting sight to so many;

15
00:01:05,379 --> 00:01:10,857
what has no capacity to hear 
is allowing everyone to hear;

16
00:01:10,857 --> 00:01:15,656
what cannot taste is giving
everyone the tasting capacity.

17
00:01:15,656 --> 00:01:19,915
We’ve swallowed 
this type of …
 

18
00:01:19,915 --> 00:01:22,915
What’s the scientific term?

19
00:01:22,915 --> 00:01:26,428
—‘Bullshit’— I think that’s 
the scientific term:

20
00:01:26,428 --> 00:01:34,308
we’ve swallowed this wholesale,
and denied the Personality of Godhead,

21
00:01:34,308 --> 00:01:39,378
and think that we’re very modern, 
very advanced scientific thinkers.

22
00:01:39,378 --> 00:01:42,772
Because we can’t accommodate 
how the original source

23
00:01:42,772 --> 00:01:47,190
of all sensual ability 
and capacity
 

24
00:01:47,190 --> 00:01:50,190
can also have 
sensual ability and capacity—

25
00:01:50,190 --> 00:01:55,605
we deny that: that’s just
that would be just too much.

26
00:01:55,605 --> 00:01:59,585
I mean that would be 
like God or something. [Laughing]

27
00:01:59,585 --> 00:02:03,697
Right,
that would be inconceivable

28
00:02:03,697 --> 00:02:09,035
that an absolute personality,
who is absolutely beautiful,

29
00:02:09,035 --> 00:02:15,992
absolutely charming, absolutely funny,
absolutely tasteful,

30
00:02:15,992 --> 00:02:23,387
who can reciprocate simultaneously 
the ideal hankering of every being—

31
00:02:23,387 --> 00:02:26,848
that would be
the Absolute, of course.

32
00:02:26,848 --> 00:02:35,089
So, that the Ultimate Reality is beautiful, 
loving, charming, and sweet:

33
00:02:35,089 --> 00:02:38,398
science is not prepared 
to deal with that.

